      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1773700518897,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Considerations: \nIf someone joins the itinerary, do they overwrite the previous version?\nShould we add the ability to control revisions? e.g., my itinerary shows\nbeaches, but 2nd person wants concerts, do concerts override the\nbeach? subsequent intake preferences should show up as suggestions\nvs overwriting the itinerary. \n",
      "fontSize": 23.49999999999999,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Considerations: \nIf someone joins the itinerary, do they overwrite the previous version? Should we add the ability to control revisions? e.g., my itinerary shows beaches, but 2nd person wants concerts, do concerts override the beach? subsequent intake preferences should show up as suggestions vs overwriting the itinerary. \n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
